{"tid":264811,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"方濟各：做虛偽教徒，不如做無神論者 !","createTime":"2017-05-31T06:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T07:25:02.000Z","uid":105678,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7ba76b20a16f5c9a91215565fe0c3ee595314d","tid":264811,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/photo/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001_01b.jpg?20170224122445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170224%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170224122445&h=e82a14d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天主教教宗方濟各周四主持彌撒時再語出驚人，直斥不少天主教徒過着虛偽的「雙面生活」，講一套做一套。教宗更指，做虛偽教徒不如做無神論者。<br />\n<br />\n梵蒂岡電台報道，教宗在寓所內主持私人彌撒時「爆肚」，嚴詞批評：「有些人會說『我非常虔誠，經常赴彌撒，我有參加這些及那些組織』，但他們應該同時說『我的生活並不表現基督精神，我不付合理薪酬予員工，我剝削他人，我做骯髒的生意，我洗黑錢，我過着雙面生活』。」<br />\n<br />\n教宗指，就是這些人造成醜聞，令人不斷聽到「如果天主教徒是這樣的話，那不如當個無神論者好了」這句說話。教宗過去曾指，做好事的無神論者不應被視為罪人，他們也可得到耶穌的救贖而上天堂，其言論震驚不少教徒。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170224%2Fbknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html&d=e9O9amzqvGH8pRtNz3tTusmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6785925f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"46be61620b9f025d42b3fcbe718bc037f8f886dc","tid":264811,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n教宗指，就是這些人造成醜聞，令人不斷聽到「如果天主教徒是這樣的話，那不如當個無神論者好了」這句說話。<span style=\"color: red;\">教宗過去曾指，做好事的無神論者不應被視為罪人，他們也可得到耶穌的救贖而上天堂，其言論震驚不少教徒。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170224%2Fbknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html&d=e9O9amzqvGH8pRtNz3tTusmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6785925f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我放心了 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb842a0b6d398ad136ad9c2c2ad596daeeb69de","tid":264811,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"我可以得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bde467edc98ff76b96a86ad7037f0c76193cf9","tid":264811,"uid":113925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢無講錯"},{"pid":"e39b4e89683a1f027639b9ca36780e239f802898","tid":264811,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n教宗指，就是這些人造成醜聞，令人不斷聽到「如果天主教徒是這樣的話，那不如當個無神論者好了」這句說話。<span style=\"color: red;\">教宗過去曾指，做好事的無神論者不應被視為罪人，他們也可得到耶穌的救贖而上天堂，其言論震驚不少教徒。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170224%2Fbknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html&d=e9O9amzqvGH8pRtNz3tTusmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6785925f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/bknint-20170224112359153-0224_17011_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我放心了 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班耶撚有咩好震驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行善積德但唔信耶穌就要落地獄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n殺人放火臨尾坐監先信耶穌就可以上天堂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833f7319bbfb2ee485d3667754b178929edd5c89","tid":264811,"uid":57409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s